# orcasecurity_user_access (Resource)

Manages a single user's permissions ("Manage User Permissions" in the UI) by assigning an RBAC role to a user with optional scope. Backed by `/api/rbac/access/user`.

This is the per-user counterpart of `orcasecurity_group_access`. To invite a new user, use `orcasecurity_add_users`.

